<view class="page-container">
  
  <view class="settings-section">
    <view class="section-title">隐私设置</view>
    
    <view class="list-group">
      <!-- 公开我的作品集 -->
      <view class="list-item">
        <view class="item-left">
          <van-icon name="photo-o" size="24px" color="#9CA3AF" custom-class="item-icon" />
          <view class="item-content">
            <text class="item-title">公开我的作品集</text>
            <text class="item-desc">允许所有用户在您的个人主页浏览设计案例</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="item-right">
          <van-switch checked="{{publicPortfolio}}" bind:change="onChangePortfolio" active-color="#000000" size="28px" />
        </view>
        <view class="divider"></view>
      </view>
      
      <!-- 允许业主发起咨询 -->
      <view class="list-item">
        <view class="item-left">
          <van-icon name="chat-o" size="24px" color="#9CA3AF" custom-class="item-icon" />
          <view class="item-content">
            <text class="item-title">允许业主发起咨询</text>
            <text class="item-desc">开启后业主可通过您的主页发送私信咨询</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="item-right">
          <van-switch checked="{{allowConsult}}" bind:change="onChangeConsult" active-color="#000000" size="28px" />
        </view>
        <view class="divider"></view>
      </view>
      
      <!-- 展示我的评分与评价 -->
      <view class="list-item">
        <view class="item-left">
          <van-icon name="star-o" size="24px" color="#9CA3AF" custom-class="item-icon" />
          <view class="item-content">
            <text class="item-title">展示我的评分与评价</text>
            <text class="item-desc">向公众展示历史合作订单的评分及客户评价</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="item-right">
          <van-switch checked="{{showRating}}" bind:change="onChangeRating" active-color="#000000" size="28px" />
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="tips-text">
      关闭后，相关信息将仅对已建立合作关系的客户可见，可能会影响您的接单机会。
    </view>
  </view>

</view>
